<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>iTEK | AirPods Pro</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#000;
color:white;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* Fondo premium */
body::before{
content:"";
position:fixed;
width:700px;
height:700px;
background:radial-gradient(circle,#0077ff 0%,transparent 70%);
top:-250px;
left:-200px;
opacity:.4;
z-index:-1;
}

body::after{
content:"";
position:fixed;
width:600px;
height:600px;
background:radial-gradient(circle,#00d4ff 0%,transparent 70%);
bottom:-250px;
right:-150px;
opacity:.25;
z-index:-1;
}

header{
padding:25px 8%;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
position:sticky;
top:0;
backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
background:rgba(0,0,0,.5);
border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
}

.logo{
font-size:32px;
font-weight:800;
letter-spacing:3px;
}

.hero{
min-height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
padding:80px 8%;
}

.hero-content{
text-align:center;
max-width:1000px;
}

.badge{
display:inline-block;
padding:10px 18px;
border-radius:30px;
background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
margin-bottom:25px;
}

.hero h1{
font-size:90px;
font-weight:800;
line-height:1;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero p{
font-size:24px;
color:#b8b8b8;
margin-bottom:35px;
}

.precio{
font-size:60px;
font-weight:700;
background:linear-gradient(90deg,#00d4ff,#0077ff);
-webkit-background-clip:text;
-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
margin-bottom:35px;
}

.btn{
display:inline-block;
padding:18px 40px;
border-radius:50px;
text-decoration:none;
font-weight:600;
font-size:18px;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0077ff,#00d4ff);
color:white;
transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
transform:translateY(-4px);
}

.product{
padding:100px 8%;
text-align:center;
}

.product img{
width:100%;
max-width:650px;
filter:drop-shadow(0 0 40px rgba(0,150,255,.5));
margin-bottom:40px;
}

.features{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:25px;
padding:0 8% 100px;
}

.card{
background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);
backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
padding:30px;
border-radius:25px;
text-align:center;
}

.card h3{
margin-bottom:10px;
}

.card p{
color:#bdbdbd;
}

footer{
padding:40px;
text-align:center;
color:#999;
border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
}

.whatsapp{
position:fixed;
right:25px;
bottom:25px;
width:70px;
height:70px;
border-radius:50%;
background:#25D366;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
font-size:30px;
text-decoration:none;
color:white;
box-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(37,211,102,.5);
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero h1{
font-size:55px;
}

.hero p{
font-size:18px;
}

.precio{
font-size:40px;
}

}

</style>

</head>
<body>

<header>
<div class="logo">iTEK</div>
</header>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-content">

<div class="badge">
✨ Nuevo lanzamiento
</div>

<h1>AirPods Pro 3</h1>

<p>
Sonido premium. Cancelación activa de ruido.
Diseñados para una experiencia extraordinaria.
</p>

<div class="precio">
Bs 340
</div>

<a class="btn"
href="https://wa.me/59163904221?text=Hola%20iTEK,%20quiero%20comprar%20los%20AirPods%20Pro%203"
target="_blank">
Comprar Ahora </a>

</div>

</section>

<section class="product">

<img src="airpods.png" alt="AirPods Pro">

</section>

<section class="features">

<div class="card">
<h3>🎧 Audio Premium</h3>
<p>Calidad de sonido envolvente y potente.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🔇 Cancelación de Ruido</h3>
<p>Escucha solo lo que quieres escuchar.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🔋 Mayor Autonomía</h3>
<p>Batería para todo el día.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>🚚 Envíos Nacionales</h3>
<p>Entregas rápidas en toda Bolivia.</p>
</div>

</section>

<footer>
© 2026 iTEK · WhatsApp +591 63904221
</footer>

<a class="whatsapp"
href="https://wa.me/59163904221"
target="_blank">
💬 </a>

</body>
</html>
